{"tid":1771902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵總監劉天成：員工面對嚴峻挑戰額外發2000元的嘉許獎","createTime":"2019-12-06T07:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T09:44:50.000Z","uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a26e1fee36d02b9adba47de379fe9311e08a9f67","tid":1771902,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】港鐵表示過去數個月，超過9成車站被破壞，有百多次遭投擲汽油彈，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: gold;\">除了對乘客不便、港鐵職員疲於奔命維修之外，還有龐大的復修開支。</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成表示，過去6個月港鐵遭受<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">40年</span></span></strong>來最嚴重的惡意破壞，估算截止11月底有關車站設施的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: gold;\">復修和更換費用大約5億元</span></em></span>。又指大學站被破壞很嚴重，所有設施全部爛了，近乎要重建。<br />\n<br />\n關閉近1個月的大學站，港鐵希望今個月底前重開，但部分出口和設施仍然要關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: maroon;\">港鐵指近數個月員工面對嚴峻挑戰，不只受辱罵，更有超過10個員工遇襲受傷，港鐵向8，000名員工每月額外發放2000元的嘉許獎。又新設附例特勤隊，以及加派保安員協助支援。</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVWMJvJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVWMJvJ.png&h=ec2de263&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qydvqJ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqydvqJ4.png&h=0c516de6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b840076bf8c6d7e220f1eaa9c39666ca0b558fe9","tid":1771902,"uid":25424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9b7dbc85ec71deae1a68eaf41e9c663fe87e73","tid":1771902,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"2000 就換到啲黃衫狗落力捉示威者"},{"pid":"f8896a14a085c224bdec756eba1aecf73395b5d7","tid":1771902,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"離國際水準仲好遠<img sr